       VIAP0013-READ-VIAF0001.
      *
            OPEN INPUT VIAF0001.

            READ VIAF0001
              AT END
                SET VIAW0013-FSTATUS-EOF TO TRUE
            END-READ.

            MOVE VIAF0001-RECORD      TO VIAW0013-DATA.

            CLOSE VIAF0001.
